title: Release date for the new project skins?

replies.body: Anywhere between Thursday 28th, July and Tuesday 2nd, August, 2016.

We don't have any information on upcoming content until it's announced.  Right now I'm enjoying the [pool party](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/patch/patch-614-notes#patch-upcoming-skins) and looking forward to an outrageous tan, but I'm ready for any new stuff coming out too!  Our [News Page](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news) will keep you updated on any new skins coming!
